id=silence-shutter-screenshot
name=Silence Shutter and Screenshot
version=2.1
versionCode=3
author=hritwik
description=Silences the camera shutter and screenshot sound by bind-mounting a short silent clip over the UI sound files (camera_click.ogg etc.) on every boot. Uses an explicit mount --bind in post-fs-data.sh instead of magic-mount, because magic-mount does not reach the separate /product partition on KernelSU 3.2.0. Systemless and fully reversible. Verified on Pixel 10a (Android 17). Third-party camera apps that bundle their own shutter sound are unaffected.
